lead_paragraph: Jeff Teague scored 22 points, Paul Millsap had 20 points and a season-high 18 rebounds, and the Atlanta Hawks beat the Los Angeles Clippers 107-97 Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Millsap, Teague Lead Hawks Over Clippers 107-97
